    <item>
      <title>由于沙特阿拉伯提高价格，油价在每周暴跌后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在一周下跌后上涨，因沙特阿拉伯连续第三个月提高向亚洲出售的原油价格，表明对 OPEC+ 卡特尔削减供应的前景充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 23:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着亚洲开盘走高，中国股市将追赶：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/asian-stocks-eye-positive-start-as-china-returns-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待中国从长假结束后重新开放，亚洲股市基准早盘小幅上涨。随着北京方面的支持性政策立场为新兴的看涨势头增添动力，内地市场似乎有望上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/asian-stocks-eye-positive-start-as-china-returns-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 22:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀加剧，澳大利亚央行预计将关键利率维持在 12 年来的高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/rba-to-keep-key-rate-at-12-year-high-as-inflation-stirs-anew</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行可能会将关键利率维持在 12 年来的高位，并在今年大部分时间里维持不变，以抑制就业市场出奇紧张所带来的通胀压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/rba-to-keep-key-rate-at-12-year-high-as-inflation-stirs-anew</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯提高向亚洲出售所有等级石油的价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/saudi-arabia-hikes-oil-selling-prices-to-asia-across-all-grades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯连续第三个月上调其对亚洲旗舰原油的价格，该国试图收紧石油市场以防止全球供应过剩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/saudi-arabia-hikes-oil-selling-prices-to-asia-across-all-grades</guid>
